    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S54 straight-six engine, renowned for its high-revving characteristics and individual throttle bodies, delivering a crisp, linear power band. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucially, this chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term structural and timing integrity. The factory suspension geometry remains tight, with no bushing deflection or damper fatigue. Finished in original Carbon Black with a flawless interior, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own an analog icon in its most pristine, mechanically sorted form.",
